      "content": "i guess. but isn't it kind of a contradiction though? if the whole point is to prevent conflict and the veto power basically makes it impossible to act when it matters most, isn't saying it's \"essential\" just a way to legitimize a broken system? feels like a way to avoid saying the institution is actually obsolete.",
